story of “firsts” that paved the way for online travel agencies corporate booking tools revenue management and web and mobile itinerary tools to name a few and we’re still blazing a trail by investing hundreds of millions of dollars each year in research and development to create the next generation of ecommerce and software as a service saas solutions for travel agencies corporations travelers airlines hotels car rail cruise and tour operator companies and while technology is at our core we also hire the best in all of the disciplines it takes to run a highlyrespected company from marketing and customer service to finance and human resources we encourage a balanced lifestyle personal wellness and community involvement we believe that a balanced life fuels greater innovation which then powers the worldleading travel solutions for which sabre is known if you’re passionate about solving complex problems in a dynamic industry join the sabre team and take your career on the journey of a lifetime search current jobs quick find featured locations all countries asia  south pacific europe middle east  africa latin america  caribbean north america india poland featured jobs technology jobs technology sales jobs software development jobs intern jobs about careers news  insights investor relations expanding capabilities for group travelers introducing airvision group optimizer « sabre search sabrecom what we do businesses sabre airline solutions sabre hospitality solutions sabre travel network technologies data solutions mobile online commerce platform services software who we serve airlines  airports car rental companies corporations cruise lines developers government hotels meta search engines online travel agencies rail carriers tour companies travel agencies travel consolidators travel management companies news  insights newsroom press releases insights blog research  intelligence innovation hub labs events about executive leadership corporate responsibility locations cont