ess travelers and  percent of north american travelers the experience affects job satisfaction either somewhat or to a great extent given the active nature of the industry many startups and other companies attempt to snag a chunk of the business traveler’s loyalty airbnb continues to make aggressive moves into the enterprise while smaller entrants such as upside are eager to make a dent in the normal way of doing business business traveltravel expert indextraveler experience nick vivion nick was the senior brand journalist for sabre from  to  hes covered the travel industry as a journalist and filmmaker for over  years prior to sabre nick was avp of operations for zomato as well as reporter and global events lead for travel trade tnooz hes been an ongoing contributor to usa today and his projects have been featured in saveur travel  leisure food  wine and apex see more articles from this author » older newer related articles blog jun   book and manage travel all from one intuitive mobile interface agencies  otas blog may   travel expert index on the airline passenger experience around the industry blog may   travel solved using design to empower road warriors to travel the way they want to corporate travel blog may   the incredible power of placing the traveler at the center of the airport experience airlines blog apr   travel expert index the state of loyalty in travel around the industry blog mar   enhancing the passenger’s digital experience through better airline ecommerce airlines blog mar   how visa increased adoption of its new travel booking tool from  to  percent corporate travel blog mar   travel expert index how is the evolution of communication impacting customer service around the industry sign me up for insights sign up for the email we promise we won’t share your email address with anyone email address about careers news  insights investor relations new research how ready are consumers for emerging technology « sabre search sabrecom what we do busines